00:01:30.015 --> 00:01:31.572
and I thought,

00:01:31.596 --> 00:01:36.506
"Oh, I'm so lucky
that I am healthy and living

00:01:36.530 --> 00:01:42.715
in a decade where we who are alive
can actually make the difference.

00:01:42.739 --> 00:01:45.639
We can make the difference

00:01:45.663 --> 00:01:48.413
as to whether there's going
to be a livable future or not.

00:01:48.437 --> 00:01:51.143
What a glorious responsibility we have.

00:01:51.167 --> 00:01:52.974
We have to step up to the plate."

00:01:52.998 --> 00:01:54.910
